---
// Privacy Policy page
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Fresh Wax privacy policy - how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  <Header />

  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-container">
      <div class="legal-header">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: December 2024</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <section>
          <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>When you use Fresh Wax, we collect:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Email address, display name, and password</li>
            <li><strong>Profile information:</strong> Artist name, bio, and links (if applicable)</li>
            <li><strong>Purchase history:</strong> Records of your transactions</li>
            <li><strong>Content:</strong> DJ mixes, comments, and ratings you submit</li>
            <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> How you interact with the platform</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide and maintain the Fresh Wax platform</li>
            <li>Process purchases and deliver digital content</li>
            <li>Enable community features (comments, ratings, mixes)</li>
            <li>Communicate with you about your account and orders</li>
            <li>Improve our services</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
          <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Payment processors:</strong> To complete transactions</li>
            <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Who help us operate the platform</li>
            <li><strong>Legal requirements:</strong> When required by law</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Your public profile, uploaded mixes, comments, and ratings are visible to other users.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>4. Data Storage</h2>
          <p>Your data is stored securely using industry-standard practices. We use Firebase and Cloudflare services to host and protect your information.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your account and data</li>
            <li>Download your uploaded content</li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise these rights, please contact us through the platform.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
          <p>We use essential cookies for authentication and session management. We may use analytics cookies to understand how the platform is used.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>Our platform may contain links to external sites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of other websites.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>Fresh Wax is not intended for users under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect information from children.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes through the platform or by email.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>10. Contact</h2>
          <p>For privacy-related questions, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a> through the platform.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-primary, #0a0a0a);
  }

  .legal-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--bg-secondary, #141414);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color, #262626);
  }

  .legal-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color, #262626);
  }

  .legal-header h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary, #fff);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--text-muted, #666);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .legal-content {
    color: var(--text-secondary, #a3a3a3);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-content section {
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .legal-content h3 {
    color: var(--text-primary, #fff);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal-content p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal-content ul {
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .legal-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .legal-content strong {
    color: var(--text-primary, #fff);
  }

  .legal-content a {
    color: #ef4444;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .legal-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
